Kellie Waymire https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kellie_Waymire 0 Kellie Suzanne Waymire (July 27, 1967 – November 13, 2003) was an American stage, television, and film actress. Two of her highest-profile roles were on Six Feet Under and on Star Trek: Enterprise.
